{"id": "1497418424773509160", "channel_id": "1495670208004882483", "type": 19, "author_id": "535648171871698965", "author_name": "watashiwawolf", "author_bot": false, "content": "what do you propose as the solution for people who like playing PvP and new players getting into PvP?\n\nThe PvP gamemode is a different experience of the game", "timestamp": "2026-04-25T02:06:13.155000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["212031841786527764"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1495677584602828810", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1495670208004882483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PVE players don't want Traphase", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1497418749958033588", "channel_id": "1495670208004882483", "type": 19, "author_id": "535648171871698965", "author_name": "watashiwawolf", "author_bot": false, "content": "yeah, the game mode is really dead they have that setting by default off, It takes a while to find a match with the settings on, i wish there was more players for it", "timestamp": "2026-04-25T02:07:30.685000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["272731767079829505"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1497418192744743013", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1495670208004882483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PVE players don't want Traphase", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1497441451888611409", "channel_id": "1495670208004882483", "type": 19, "author_id": "250664395749720065", "author_name": "_pdt", "author_bot": false, "content": "Any alternative is fine.\n\nGive an option for PVE players to fight bots.\n\nChange the condition to participation like \"play 5 minutes\" or \"15 cards in Traphase\" instead of WIN.\n(Just \"join a match\" means many people like me are 100% going to join a match and concede ASAP. Nothing against this solution because it solves my problems, but as much as I grew into not liking this mode, I don't think it's a good design...)\n\nPersonally, I'd rather have those rewards with an option. P-Dive is 3x a week, every week. All Pick is 5 wins every 2 weeks and Draft, 5 wins every 4 weeks. It would be awesome if I could just play P-Dive more than 3x a week and get all . And whoever likes PvP, could do the same.", "timestamp": "2026-04-25T03:37:43.247000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-25T03:41:14.487000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["535648171871698965"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1497418424773509160", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1495670208004882483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PVE players don't want Traphase", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"]}
